      "severity": "MAJOR-REVISION",
      "justification": "If confirmed, the manuscript overstates how directly existing infrastructure can validate the framework. This is a real methodological gap in the proposed empirical agenda, but it is revisable by specifying what additional data/experimental design would actually be needed."
    },
