      "severity": "MAJOR-REVISION",
      "justification": "If confirmed, the generalization of the formal results to the motivating applications is methodologically questionable. The formal setup may fit benchmark tasks but not many of the paper's stated domains. This limits conclusions rather than fully invalidating them."
    },
